annotationA: Nesthocker (Nst) is a phospho-acetylglucosamine mutase, an essential enzyme in the biosynthetic pathway of N-Acetylglucosamine (GlcNAc). In the embryo Nst is required for normal GlcNAc levels and affects Fibroblast-Growth-Factor signaling
annotationB: N-acetyltransferase activity; glucosamine 6-phosphate N-acetyltransferase activity; Belongs to the acetyltransferase family. GNA1 subfamily
